msgid "Wi-Fi 和 ESP-BLE-MESH 共存时，支持哪些模式？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:19
#: eb94c8acfd7e426b8aaf413d952d789b
msgid "目前，只有 Wi-Fi STA 模式支持共存。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:24
#: f95feef5e2804ec3bd2470253866313d
msgid "Wi-Fi 和 ESP-BLE-MESH 共存时，为什么 Wi-Fi 吞吐量很低？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:26
#: d931b4363eaf4a27a065e1d6548ed72c
msgid ""
"未搭载 PSRAM 的 ESP32-DevKitC 开发板，Wi-Fi 和 ESP-BLE-MESH 共存可以正常运行，但是吞吐率较低。当 Wi-"
"Fi 和 ESP-BLE-MESH 共存时，搭载 PSRAM 的 ESP32-DevKitC 速率可以稳定在 1 Mbps 以上。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:28
#: 3373c929d13b43e187a6b90591ffa1bc
msgid "应使能 menuconfig 中的一些配置来支持 PSRAM:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:30
#: 03535db9026c499f858d285e1d24a8b8
msgid ""
"``ESP32-specific --> Support for external,SPI-connected RAM --> Try to "
"allocate memories of Wi-Fi and LWIP...``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:31
#: 5398a668dbb74aa2b47ca5128be6669a
msgid ""
"``Bluetooth --> Bluedriod Enable --> BT/BLE will first malloc the memory "
"from the PSRAM``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:32
#: 44f3776135de48339762aaa6334d0215
msgid ""
"``Bluetooth --> Bluedriod Enable --> Use dynamic memory allocation in "
"BT/BLE stack.``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:33
#: fe965edf2bc0425c89868448c1716489
msgid "``Bluetooth --> Blutooth controller --> BLE full scan feature supported.``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/coexistence.rst:34
#: efd2b3300d7f4e979630c50c61f8d3c6
msgid "``Wi-Fi --> Software controls Wi-Fi/Bluetooth coexistence --> Wi-Fi``"
msgstr ""

